flowchart LR
  V["Incoming vote<br/>{ ip, ua, browserToken }"] --> T["Trim ring<br/>(5-min window)"]
  T --> S1{Same IP<br/>burst?}
  S1 -->|≥3 in 60s| W1[+40]
  S1 -->|≥1 in 60s| W2[+15]
  T --> S2{Same /24<br/>burst?}
  S2 -->|≥8 in 60s| W3[+30]
  T --> S3{UA reused<br/>≥6× in 5min?}
  S3 -->|yes| W4[+15]
  T --> S4{IP density<br/>≥12 / 5min?}
  S4 -->|yes| W5[+20]
  T --> S5{Thin UA?}
  S5 -->|yes| W6[+10]

  W1 & W2 & W3 & W4 & W5 & W6 --> SUM["Total score"]
  SUM --> C1{score ≥ 60?}
  C1 -->|yes| HIGH["severity = high<br/>→ exclude from People's Choice"]
  C1 -->|no| C2{score ≥ 30?}
  C2 -->|yes| MED[severity = medium]
  C2 -->|no| C3{score ≥ 10?}
  C3 -->|yes| LOW[severity = low]
  C3 -->|no| NONE[severity = none]
